# Performance

Always optimize for Core Web Vitals.

## Rendering

- Avoid unnecessary re-renders.
- Avoid expensive computations inside render.
- Use `React.memo` only when beneficial.
- Use `useMemo` only for expensive calculations.
- Use `useCallback` only when function identity matters.

## Images

- Next.js Image.
- Lazy loading.
- Responsive images.
- Blur placeholders.

## Dynamic Imports

- Lazy load heavy components.
- Use code splitting.

## Bundle

- Tree shaking.
- Avoid unnecessary libraries.
- Prefer lightweight alternatives.

## Lists

- Virtualize long lists.
- Stable keys.

## CSS

- Avoid large CSS files.
- Prefer Tailwind utility classes.
- Extract reusable styles.

## Network

- Debounce search.
- Throttle scroll.
- Cache requests.
- Avoid duplicate requests.

